items.name: ESEA OCE Cash Cup Summer 1
items.description:
**General Rules**

- Agent skins are NOT allowed, anyone reported for using an agent skin will have their match overturned.
- Once the registration is closed, no changes are allowed on the roster. Make sure to add all the players/substitutes/coach to your roster.
- Users with a Game-Ban on their FACEIT account will NOT be able to play on this qualifier, they will still be able to sign up but they will not be able to play.


**Format** (depending on the number of teams taking part)

- Up to 4 teams: Semifina≈Çs (Bo3) and Final (Bo3) on Day 1
- 5-16 teams: 1/8 (Bo1), Quarterfinals (Bo1), and Semifinals (Bo3) on Day 1. Final (Bo3) on Day 2
- More than 16 teams: All rounds up to and including Quarterfinals (Bo1) on Day 1. Semifinals (Bo3), and Final (Bo3) on Day 2


Day 2 matches start at the same time as Day 1.


**Registration**

- Registration/check-in will close 5 minutes before the event is set to start. Once it's closed, teams are NOT allowed to make any changes/add additional players.
- Check-in will open 1 hour before the event is set to start

IEM Sydney 2023 - Oceania Open Qualifier 1
items.description:
- Two open qualifiers, one closed qualifier
- 4 teams in closed qualifier, 2 teams from open, 2 invited
- Open qualifier #1: 9-10 August (start time 18:00 AEST)
- Open qualifier #2: 11-12 August (start time 18:00 AEST)
- One team advances to the closed qualifier from each open qualifier
- OQ format: unlimited SE best-of-one bracket with decider match being played in Bo3.
- Closed qualifier: 22-23 August (matches at 16:30 and 21:00 AEST)
- 1 team from closed qualifier advances to the main event
- CQ format: DE best-of-three bracket.
